description: --- license: apache-2.0 pipeline_tag: sentence-similarity --- ONNX port of sentence-transformers/all-MiniLM-L6-v2 for text classification and similarity searches. ### Usage Here's an example of performing inference using the model with FastEmbed. > Note: This model is supposed to be used with Qdrant. Vectors have to be configured with Modifier.IDF.
model_explanation_gemini: An ONNX-optimized version of all-MiniLM-L6-v2 for text classification and similarity searches, designed for use with Qdrant's vector search requiring IDF-weighted vectors.
